name: Anchor, Reykjavik, Iceland
description: This monument sits on the coastline in the city of Reykjavik, Iceland and I snapped this photo when I was there for New Years Eve and the first week of January 2019.  I loved the way the 3:30 pm sunset was lighting it up!  This was listed as a 500 edition drop and burn, the NFT was minted and dropped and all leftovers burned after 2.5 hours, so we shall see how many are left in the end!
